title: 262: Would We Be Friends If We Met As Adults? | Ear Biscuits Ep.262
description:
What if Rhett and Link never met in first grade? What if instead, they had met as adults? Listen to the guys guess what their first interaction may be like, the struggles of making friends as adults, and if they would actually still become friends had they met today in this episode of Ear Biscuits!
